post_install(){
 cat <<INFO

To complete the installation of App Route Jail, run two commands,
assuming 192.168.1.1  is your router:

    sudo ip rule add fwmark 10 table 100
    sudo ip route add default via 192.168.1.1 table 100

Then, launch your application (e.g. firefox) by prepending the library:

    MARK=10 LD_PRELOAD=/usr/lib/mark.so firefox

INFO
}
